snippet: OSBORNE--Alan, MD, Radiologist, 84, Dr. Alan Osborne, a long time Westfield resident, passed away on April 6, 2016, at his home. Dr. Osborne graduated from Princeton University Phi Beta Kappa and from Columbia University College of Physicians and Surgeons AOA. Following internship and residency at Presbyterian Hospital and service in the Air Force, he was a radiologist at Rahway Hospital, now Robert Wood Johnson Hospital, and Children's Specialized Hospital for over 30 years. Dr. Osborne's wife, Bernice, passed away in 2003. He is survived by seven children, Jeanne, Jim, Bob, Anne, Mike, John and Tom, their spouses, and five grandchildren. 1/3
